Earthseeker				KEY:Bloodcrier's Hammer ~ Earthseeker		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 6th level and higher, while wielding Bloodcrier's Hammer, you can detect any creature with the earth subtype within 60 feet. You must concentrate (a standard action) to do so. The hammer ignores any damage reduction an earth-subtype creature possesses.						SOURCEPAGE:p.30		ASPECT:CombatBonus|Bloodcrier's Hammer ignores DR of earth-subtype creatures.
Pathbreaker				KEY:Bloodcrier's Hammer ~ Pathbreaker		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:Beginning at 7th level, once per day when Bloodcrier's Hammer is struck against a lock, lid, door, valve, portal, normal bars, shackles, chains, bolts, and so on, a mournful tone rings forth. The struck item opens 1 round later. Bloodcrier's Hammer also automatically dispels a hold portal spell or even an arcane lock with a caster level lower than 15th. Each strike opens only one form of locking, so if a chest is chained, padlocked, locked, and arcane locked, it takes four strikes to open it. A silence spell negates this power.						SOURCEPAGE:p.30
