The Earth Provides				KEY:Bloodcrier's Hammer ~ The Earth Provides		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 9th level and higher, you need not eat or drink while underground or in any place with the earth-dominant elemental trait.						SOURCEPAGE:p.31
